{"tid":2296563,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"機箱撚入 傾下用緊咩箱","createTime":"2020-11-22T14:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-22T14:41:37.000Z","uid":182543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"52bfc679a729c458d282a2d7c4b2ee21c6d37d72","tid":2296563,"uid":182543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"或者諗住換新箱?咩原因換定係身痕想試新箱?<br />\n新卡長厚又熱，換卡時會唔會想換埋機箱?<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">ITX用緊A1 PLUS(無線叉幾方便，換唔到厚卡)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.in-win.com/media/gaming-chassis/a1-plus/20190226024532_37243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.in-win.com%2Fmedia%2Fgaming-chassis%2Fa1-plus%2F20190226024532_37243.jpg&h=83e73285&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想換280X(可放大牛但就入風出風麻麻)<br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.neweggimages.com/ProductImage/11-139-130-01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.neweggimages.com%2FProductImage%2F11-139-130-01.jpg&h=01981e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者011D MINI($800幾抵玩12月先有貨，要用SFX牛，要睇住隻牛做人，多數最大得750W，1000W得銀欣未知幾時出)<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.wccftech.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/VhwulcMNdxdg6j2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wccftech.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F11%2FVhwulcMNdxdg6j2W.jpg&h=ebd26b12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姑媽有仇，NR200最後先諗<br />\n<img src=\"https://preview.redd.it/6wzkp3ap3eu51.jpg?width=4032&amp;format=pjpg&amp;auto=webp&amp;s=05c3a5ce069ebed7f449a1ba16ccbdcaf50c3b3f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpreview.redd.it%2F6wzkp3ap3eu51.jpg%3Fwidth%3D4032%26format%3Dpjpg%26auto%3Dwebp%26s%3D05c3a5ce069ebed7f449a1ba16ccbdcaf50c3b3f&h=eaab2fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">ATX由570X(吸塵機)轉左P600S(靜)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.corsair.com/corsairmedia/sys_master/productcontent/cc-9011110-ww-570x_rgb_wht_dimensions.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.corsair.com%2Fcorsairmedia%2Fsys_master%2Fproductcontent%2Fcc-9011110-ww-570x_rgb_wht_dimensions.png&h=1572bb62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71GSeguzg0L._AC_SL1500_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F71GSeguzg0L._AC_SL1500_.jpg&h=c6e910c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">另一ATX用緊HELIOS(玩厭左覺得阻Q住)</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://c1.neweggimages.com/ProductImageCompressAll1280/11-173-039-V04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fc1.neweggimages.com%2FProductImageCompressAll1280%2F11-173-039-V04.jpg&h=fc86bb14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想換011D XL(但係唔細得幾多)<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/LIAN-LI-0PC-O11D-XL-ROG-Certified/LIAN-LI-0PC-O11D-XL-ROG-Certified-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FLIAN-LI-0PC-O11D-XL-ROG-Certified%2FLIAN-LI-0PC-O11D-XL-ROG-Certified-2.jpg&h=0145e440&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}